Detailed Description

cvmx_gpio_xbit_cfg#

Notes: Only first 16 GPIO pins can introduce interrupts, GPIO_XBIT_CFG16(17,18,19)[INT_EN] and [INT_TYPE] will not be used, read out always zero.
